veripy
======

veripy is a tool for verifying the compliance of ICT Equipment against the
requirements for IPv6 set out in RIPE-501.

For more information about veripy, see the project website: http://veripy.org/
or follow us on Twitter: @veripyv6

Copyright (C) 2012 MWR InfoSecurity.


Installation and Usage
----------------------

For detailed installation and usage information, please refer to the Operator's
Guide.


